-- Applied Materials Says Gary Dickerson Replaces Splinter as CEO
-- B y   A r i   L e v y
-- 2013-08-15T20:10:20Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-08-15/applied-materials-says-gary-dickerson-replaces-splinter-as-ceo.html
Applied Materials Inc. said that
Gary Dickerson is replacing Michael Splinter as chief executive
officer.  Dickerson will become president and CEO on Sept. 1, and
Splinter will assume the role of executive chairman, the  Santa
Clara , California-based company said today in a statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ari Levy in San Francisco at 
